com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os
Interface WindowsLocalService

All Superinterfaces:
com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.DeployModelObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
WindowsLocalServiceImpl
public interface WindowsLocalService
extends com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability

A representation of the model object 'Windows Local Service'.

The following features are supported:

  • Dependant Components
  • Error Control
  • Executable Path
  • Log On As System
  • Run Program
  • Service Account
  • Service Account Password
  • Service Dependencies
  • Service Description
  • Service Display Name
  • Service Name
  • Service Status
  • Start Params
  • Startup Type

See Also:
OsPackage.getWindowsLocalService()
